{"title":"旅店新风","authors":["段纪夫　白彦花"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":10,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅店新风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段纪夫画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白彦花诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿耿一片心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅店树新风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸把客迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分南和北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论工农兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住到旅店里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一家人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷勤来招待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处都关心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难留自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方便送别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生病不要紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有看护人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端来茶和饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慰问一声声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣破有人补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主动找上门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红手又巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走线又飞针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作客不寂寞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他乡不思亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围坐在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习又谈心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级情意深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民服务员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可敬又可钦。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个星期天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情同一家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"份外的工作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能忘记过去"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}